Yerina CHRISTIAN, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
OCWEN LOAN SERVICING, LLC, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-1293 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 23, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed because of the appellant's failure to satisfy this court's April 4, 2018 fee order.

Appellee's motion to dismiss is denied as moot.

NORTHCUTT, LUCAS, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
